# Exercise 001 - Explore the various OpenShift elements

1) Using eval make yourself able to launch oc commands pointing Minishift;

2) Login into Minishift as developer, admin and system:admin and see for which
   of these users you are able to get info;

3) Now, as system:admin enable the admin user to have the same powers and
   verify the new enablement has been successful;

4) Using eval make yourself able to launch docker commands pointing Minishift's
   registry;

5) Check which environment variables make you able to connect to another docker
   engine and test it works;
